SAP MM (material management)
     
	 SAP MM (Materials Management) is an SAP module used to manage procurement (purchasing), inventory, and material management within an organization. 
	 It ensures that the right materials are available at the right time and at the right cost.

     In simple terms, SAP MM manages the complete process of buying materials, receiving them, storing them, and paying the vendor.
	 
