Plant                 ---> Place where operational or manufacting activities happening.

Storage location      ---> Physically where stocks or gods are stored.

Purchase organization ---> Team who are involved in the purchasing activities.

Purchase group        ---> Single person within the purchasing team.


Assignment

1)Assign Company Code to Company                   ---> OX16
2)Assign Plant to Company Code                     ---> OX18
3)Assign Purchasing Organization to Plant          ---> OX17 
4)Assign Purchasing Organization to Company Code   ---> OX01



1) PLANTS  ----->  COMPANY CODE

--> One Company code can have multiple plants
--> One Plant cannot be assigned to multiple Company codes

2) STORAGE LOCATION ----->  PLANT

--> One Plant can have multiple storage locations
--> One Storage location can be assigned to multiple Plants

3) PURCHASE ORGANIZATION  ----->  COMPANY CODE , PLANT		

--> One Purchase Organization can be assigned to multiple Company codes ( Not directly , but for plants).
-->	One Company code can have multiple Purchase Organizations.
--> One Purchase Organization can be assigned to multiple Plants.
--> One Plant can have multiple Purchase Organizations.


