Business Partner :-
	
	A Business Partner is a central master data object in SAP S/4HANA that represents a person, organization, or group with whom 
	the company does business. A Business Partner can perform multiple roles, such as Supplier and Customer.                        ---> BP
	
	
	     General role  ---> 000000
		 Accounting    ---> FLVN00
		 Purchasing    ---> FLVN01
	   
	   
	   Tables :-
	   
	   LFA1  --->  Vendor General data
	   LFB1  --->  Vendor Company Code
	   LFM1  --->  Vendor Purchasing Data
	   
	   
	   OBD3  --->  Vendor Account Group and Screen Layouts
	   FS03  --->  G/L Account
	   OBAS  --->  Assign number range to vendor account group
	   
	   
